name: Vessels 038: RAVAGE – THE PIRATE KING
description: A makeshift throne room in a pirate hideout. Through missing sections of hull we can see the dizzying drop to the city below. Ravage, the pirate king is standing on a throne made of scrap. Mutated and hideous thanks to exposure to the ship’s damaged fuel lines, Ravage is every inch the monster on the outside that he is on the inside.
